Interface CvTermEnricher<C extends CvTerm>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MIEnricher<C>
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface CvTermEnricher<C extends CvTerm>
extends MIEnricher<C>
    The CvTerm enricher is an enricher which can enrich either single cvTerm or a collection. A cvTerm enricher must be initiated with a fetcher. Sub enrichers: none.
    Since:
    13/05/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
